openModeller,is,a,program,for,performing,species,niche,modelling,simulations,It,does,so,by,building,a,representation,of,the,ecological,requirements,for,a,species,and,extrapolating,those,requirements,into,a,geographical,region,openModeller,makes,its,ecological,niche,modelling,functions,available,as,a,SOAP,based,API,to,facilitate,standardized,online,use